01:13:02,836 --> 01:13:04,129
These stones?

750
01:13:06,798 --> 01:13:10,218
- Aren't they heavy?
- Stones are beautiful.

751
01:13:15,974 --> 01:13:18,101
Stop the carriage.

752
01:13:18,184 --> 01:13:21,396
- What is it?
