771
01:14:26,378 --> 01:14:27,963
It's true.

772
01:14:28,046 --> 01:14:31,466
The sea looks like a blue streak.

773
01:14:31,549 --> 01:14:32,968
Uncle, you pissed in your pants!

774
01:14:33,051 --> 01:14:34,886
Shut up!

775
01:14:34,970 --> 01:14:37,097
