808
01:16:58,571 --> 01:17:02,033
- What's he shouting?
- I didn't understand.

809
01:17:02,492 --> 01:17:05,829
Uncle Teo's up a tree!

810
01:17:08,206 --> 01:17:11,918
I want a woman!

